{"tid":772531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】蔡少芬囍匯獲承租 月租2.25萬回報率3.6厘","createTime":"2018-08-08T23:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T23:39:06.000Z","uid":48905,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7e26f6e6315c5abc69c29e60f8da55830c0e8875","tid":772531,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T23:58:31.000Z","msg":"圈中打工仔多籮籮，蔡少芬屬其中一個。早於5年前已入市的蔡少芬，睇中前身為囍帖街的灣仔樓花新盤囍匯，一擲756.9萬元購入2座一個高層單位收租，實用面積339呎，呎價2.23萬元。近期暑假租務旺季，據聞蔡少芬持有的囍匯單位，剛以月租2.25萬元租出，實用呎租66元，以她5年前購入價計算，租務回報率有3.6厘，算是不俗。她過去五年內已4度入市，持有物業尚有尖沙嘴九龍站的凱旋門，元朗爾巒洋房等。<br />\n<br />\n踏入七月，暑假租務熱潮，租務成交暢旺，代理指，囍匯本月錄得30宗租務成交，當中不乏呎租逾70元租務個案，1座低層G室，實用面積552方呎，月租4萬元，呎租72.5元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/075726_fe1ece7675bb1baebd7f71de5c5584d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F075726_fe1ece7675bb1baebd7f71de5c5584d1.png&h=a901d825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 蔡少芬持有多個物業，堪稱圈中富婆之一</span>"},{"pid":"880b0be45f1ac995d8375bb22847816409f7958a","tid":772531,"uid":146435,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其中一半物業都係大劉送</span>"},{"pid":"c5a5b2d2a69acefe8558edcad197234e1c21b82b","tid":772531,"uid":4285,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:00:45.000Z","msg":"你對 Ada 唔好咩"},{"pid":"92458f8e621a356e35a304c8cc7a806b2bf71f76","tid":772531,"uid":17545,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"880b0be45f1ac995d8375bb22847816409f7958a","tid":772531,"uid":146435,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其中一半物業都係大劉送</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大劉送畀佢果d一早畀佢個爛賭老母敗曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse